casebody.data:
COMMONWEALTH
v.
Denny MARTINEZ. 18-P-1036 Appeals Court of Massachusetts. Entered: May 20, 2019

On the charges of unlawful possession of a firearm and unlawful possession of a loaded firearm, the judgments are vacated, and the verdicts are set aside. On the charge of unlawful possession of a high capacity loading device, the judgment is affirmed.
